Hello! I am Mayank Rajani, Founder of Project Dark Horse.

I believe in the core principles of web3, DeFi and libertarianism. I intend to create India's first public blockchain which is not a shameless copy of the Western standards.

I am heavily inspired by the shows Mr. Robot, Black Mirror and Altered Carbon.

AI and blockchain are inter-connected. Vitalik created ETH years ago with efficient mathematical constructs. I intend to create a chain whose data is readable by human beings as well.

Sadda Haq, Aithe Rakh!
